| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0306 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8aa6b0bd-919e-5ff9-8ccd-9f5efa938331"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
